metadata.name: I - The Numbers that Breathe
metadata.description:
:( 
The CEO of the number company was revealed to be a dog, the janitor was actually a millionaire, and the town's notorious troublemaker turned out to be the town's beloved granny. The twist turned the town upside down and everyone realized that numbers don't define a person's worth or character. From then on, they all made an effort to get to know each other beyond their numbers and the community became closer than ever before  
                                                        :)           
3.14159265359
